Name: Season Match
About the game: The story of Season Match starts when the Snow Queen has her magic mirror broken, and decides to make cold winter stay forever in the fairy-land. You will set out on a legendary journey to find the pieces of the broken mirror, put them together and beat the Snow Queen. Four seasons Over 250 missions Fantastic characters Easy-to-Play for all ages Learn-as-you-play tutorial Awesome music
